oken operator\">=</span>/postgresql-17.2 --with-openssl <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--sysconfdir</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/postgresql-17.2/data</code></pre></div>\n<p><em>configure: error: ICU library not found</em> 에러 발생시 <em>--without-icu</em> 옵션을 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> ./configure <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--prefix</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/postgresql-17.2 --with-openssl <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--sysconfdir</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/postgresql-17.2/data --without-icu</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"컴파일-및-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BB%B4%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"컴파일 및 설치 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a><strong><em>컴파일 및 설치</em></strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\